### Third-Party Licenses & Open Source Attribution

Pluto Agent Browser builds upon and integrates several open-source technologies:

1. **Browser-Use** (MIT License) — Core browser automation engine and agent framework.
   - Copyright (c) 2024 Gregor Zunic
   - License: MIT

2. **Electron** (MIT License) — Desktop application framework.
   - Copyright (c) Electron contributors & OpenJS Foundation
   - License: MIT

3. **uBlock Origin / Ghostery Adblocker Engine** (MPL-2.0 / MIT License) — Fast content filtering & stealth shield.
   - Copyright (c) Ghostery & uBlock Origin contributors
   - License: MPL-2.0 / MIT

4. **FastAPI & Pydantic** (MIT License) — High-performance backend API and data validation framework.
   - Copyright (c) Sebastián Ramírez & Pydantic contributors
   - License: MIT
